* Iron Raptor then looked back at Hell Beast and growled, as Iris took care 
of the invading Predacon's she would take care of this one!
She raised her sword and brought it down at Hell Beast's chest-plate, the 
sword glew red as it headed for the Predacon commander!*

* Iris continued to fire at the oncoming Predacons, she then activated a 
larger power supply and soon the auto-guns were firing more powerful charges 
at the invading Predacons. She had to save the Ark, her main function!*
